---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Wholesale Voice Termination | Global SIP Trunking - My Call Connect" description="Premium A-Z wholesale voice termination and SIP trunking. Connect globally with crystal clear quality and competitive rates for your business.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-ring ring-1 hide-on-mobile"></div>
      <div class="hero-ring ring-2 hide-on-mobile"></div>
      
      <div class="hero-content animate-up">
        <span class="badge">Global Connectivity</span>
        <h1>Wholesale Voice & <br><span class="text-gradient">SIP Trunking</span></h1>
        <p class="delay-1 animate-up">Premium A-Z voice termination with direct interconnects. Experience crystal clear quality, unlimited scalability, and competitive rates for your global communication needs.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta delay-2 animate-up">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Rates <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg></a>
          <a href="#features" class="text-link">Explore Features</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="features">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Premium <span class="text-gradient-primary">Voice Features</span></h2>
        <p>Built for carriers, enterprises, and contact centers demanding the highest quality.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <!-- CLI Routes -->
        <div class="card card-hover-effect">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Premium CLI Routes</h3>
          <p>100% Caller ID delivery guaranteed. Ideal for banks, OTPs, and brand identity preservation.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-gray-500 mb-6 list-none">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Guaranteed CLI</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> High ASR/ACD</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Direct Routes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Global Coverage -->
        <div class="card card-hover-effect">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"></line><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>A-Z Termination</h3>
          <p>Connect to any number in the world. Our extensive network covers over 190 countries.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-gray-500 mb-6 list-none">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> 500+ Interconnects</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Tier-1 Carriers</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Redundant Paths</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- SIP Trunking -->
        <div class="card card-hover-effect">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><rect x="2" y="14" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="6.01" y2="6"></line><line x1="6" y1="18" x2="6.01" y2="18"></line></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Elastic SIP Trunking</h3>
          <p>Scale your voice capacity instantly. Pay only for what you use with our flexible SIP solutions.</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-gray-500 mb-6 list-none">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Instant Provisioning</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Unlimited Channels</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Fraud Protection</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="content-image">
          <div class="content-icon">
            <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 10 10A10 10 0 0 0 12 2zm0 18a8 8 0 1 1 8-8 8 8 0 0 1-8 8z"></path><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Real-Time Analytics</h3>
          <p>Monitor your traffic with our advanced dashboard.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose Our <span class="text-gradient-primary">Voice Network?</span></h2>
          <p class="section-desc">We understand that voice quality directly impacts your business reputation. That's why we've built a robust, redundant network designed for excellence.</p>
          
          <div class="feature-list mt-8">
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-item-num">01</div>
              <div>
                <h3>HD Audio Quality</h3>
                <p>Support for G.711, G.729, and G.722 codecs ensures your calls sound crystal clear, every time.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-item-num">02</div>
              <div>
                <h3>24/7 NOC Support</h3>
                <p>Our Network Operations Center monitors traffic around the clock to prevent and resolve issues instantly.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item">
              <div class="feature-item-num">03</div>
              <div>
                <h3>Automated Routing</h3>
                <p>Smart LCR (Least Cost Routing) engine ensures you always get the best quality at the lowest possible rate.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container-sm">
      <div class="cta-box">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <span class="badge badge-light">Start Saving Today</span>
          <h2>Ready to Upgrade Your Voice Connectivity?</h2>
          <p>Download our full rate sheet and start testing our routes with a free credit.</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mt-8">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-light">Contact Sales</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-white">Download Rates</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
